OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, National Public Radio (NPR) has        
OL,6, announced that it will stop using      
OL,7, Twitter in a row over how its account  
OL,8, is described.                          
OL,10,FThe US not-for-profit news organisation
OL,11,Fclashed with the social media platform 
OL,12,Fover its decision to describe the      
OL,13,Foutlet as "government-funded media".   
OL,15,FNPR says it undermines its credibility,
OL,16,Fas US government funding accounts for  
OL,17,Fless than 1% of its budget.            
OL,19,FTwitter owner Elon Musk has promised to
OL,20,Fchange the label on the BBC's account. 
